sort of environment, too. What kind of color,

00:02:57.540 --> 00:03:06.540
coloration, design would be conducive to that
kind of activity. Work that is in public space,

00:03:06.540 --> 00:03:14.490
like thisÉI think people are able to come
to it and to painting in a much more open,

00:03:14.490 --> 00:03:19.330
generous, and quicker way. ItÕs immediate.
ItÕs the body feels the painting.

